EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN coalesce(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE CAST(substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),1,4)||'-'||substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),5,2)||'-'||substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),7,2)||' '||substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),10,2)||':'||substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),12,2)||':'||substring(trim(DATEOFBIRTH),14,2)AS TIMESTAMP)+ INTERVAL '7' HOUR END

CASE WHEN coalesce(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),1,4)||'-'||substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),5,2)||'-'||substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),7,2)||' '||substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),10,2)||':'||substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),12,2)||':'||substring(trim(REGISTEREDDATE),14,2) END
